## Clinical Significance
Conclusion: The results did not support the efficacy of PUFA in the 
treatment of ADHD, and adding PUFAs to the therapeutic regimen of ADHD is not recommended at the moment. (J. of Att. 
Dis. 2012; XX(X) 1-XX)
